{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/GifMeteoritos2.gif?t=1726392947\" /><br><br>Defend against Gods and mythological creatures with your cards in this <i>Roguelike Deckbuilder</i> game. Modify your deck as your adventure goes on to kill the God that gave you life and your cards.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/GifHadarotTienda.gif?t=1726392947\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Deck Building for Sale</i>: Buy, sell and exchange cards cheaply! Find hundreds of buyable cards for your deck and sell the ones that don't fit well with your deck. A good combination ensures a dead God!<br><br></li><li> <i>Time is linear</i>: Killing God has never been easy, nor repetitive! Spot different enemies, different cards, chests and even the bosses change with each adventure you go on!<br><br></li><li> <i>Some unique cards...</i> Passive cards will change your adventure, making it more interesting and easier. Make a sun appear on the table, allow your troops to train a little to gain strength, or maybe they need a change of teeth to bite better, you never know!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/BalanzaGif2gif.gif?t=1726392947\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Choose your path:</i> You can go classic and kill God, but if you're feeling wild go for Satan, but you can also even the scales to get the attention of Justice and break all the rules. Your choice!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hadarot (Early Acces) contains:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Two main characters, each with an unique deck of 20 cards.<br></li><li> More than 90 cards of 5 different types.<br></li><li> Other more than 60 passive cards.<br></li><li> Over 50 enemies, mini bosses and unique bosses.</li></ul></li></ul>","achi